  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the study is to compare clinical outcomes from LASIK and SBK using
      FDA-approved laser technology on the same patient
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients undergoing bilateral refractive surgery on the same day will have one eye randomized
      to LASIK and the fellow eye assigned to SBK treatment.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
